Sawyerwood was first classified as a CDP in the [[United States 2010 census|2010 census]], which recorded a population of 1,540 people.<ref>{{cite web |title=Ohio: 2010 - Population and Housing Unit Counts |url=https://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/cph-2-37.pdf |publisher=United States Census Bureau |accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>

At the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 1,382 people living the CDP, a drop of 158 from the previous census.<ref>[https://data.census.gov/all?q=sawyerwood+ohio Sawyerwood CDP, Ohio] – [[United States Census Bureau]]</ref>
